---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout title="もっと充実したテニスライフを実現">

  <!-- ===== HERO ===== -->
  <section class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <img src={`${base}images/hero/court.jpg`} alt="" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-primary-dark/80 via-primary-dark/60 to-primary-dark/90"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-32 w-full">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <p class="text-accent font-bold tracking-[0.3em] text-sm mb-6">TENNIS SCHOOL IN SAPPORO</p>
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-8xl font-black text-white mb-8 leading-[1.1] tracking-tight">
          御忍庭球塾
        </h1>
        <div class="w-16 h-0.5 bg-accent mb-8"></div>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-white/80 leading-relaxed mb-12 max-w-lg">
          札幌市白石区を拠点に、少人数制レッスンで<br />
          一人ひとりの上達をサポートします
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <a href={`${base}courses`} class="border border-accent text-accent hover:bg-accent hover:text-primary-dark font-bold px-10 py-4 transition text-center tracking-wider">
            コース・料金
          </a>
          <a href="https://lin.ee/2CKErIS" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="border border-white/40 text-white hover:bg-white/10 font-bold px-10 py-4 transition text-center tracking-wider">
            体験のお申し込み
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- Scroll indicator -->
    <div class="absolute bottom-8 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 flex flex-col items-center gap-2 text-white/50">
      <span class="text-xs tracking-[0.2em]">SCROLL</span>
      <div class="w-px h-10 bg-white/30 animate-pulse"></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== NEWS ===== -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-end md:justify-between mb-16">
        <div>
          <p class="text-[5rem] md:text-[7rem] font-black text-primary/5 leading-none -mb-6 md:-mb-8">NEWS</p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold relative">お知らせ</h2>
        </div>
        <a href={`${base}blog`} class="mt-6 md:mt-0 text-primary font-bold border-b border-primary pb-1 hover:opacity-70 transition inline-flex items-center gap-2">
          一覧へ <span class="text-lg">→</span>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="divide-y divide-gray-200">
        <a href={`${base}blog`} class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center gap-2 sm:gap-8 py-5 hover:opacity-70 transition">
          <time class="text-sm text-text-light whitespace-nowrap">2026.02.07</time>
          <span class="text-sm text-accent font-bold">ご案内</span>
          <span class="font-medium">出欠マニュアル</span>
        </a>
        <a href={`${base}blog`} class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center gap-2 sm:gap-8 py-5 hover:opacity-70 transition">
          <time class="text-sm text-text-light whitespace-nowrap">2025.10.09</time>
          <span class="text-sm text-accent font-bold">ご報告</span>
          <span class="font-medium">瀧野詩穂さん・長野友美さんが A級部門 準優勝！全国大会へ進出！</span>
        </a>
        <a href={`${base}blog`} class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center gap-2 sm:gap-8 py-5 hover:opacity-70 transition">
          <time class="text-sm text-text-light whitespace-nowrap">2025.10.09</time>
          <span class="text-sm text-accent font-bold">ご報告</span>
          <span class="font-medium">北海道テニス選手権 & 全日本テニス選手権 北海道予選 結果報告</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== ABOUT ===== -->
  <section class="relative py-32 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-dark to-primary"></div>
    <p class="absolute top-8 left-4 md:left-12 text-[5rem] md:text-[10rem] font-black text-white/[0.03] leading-none tracking-tight">ABOUT</p>
    <div class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="aspect-[4/3] overflow-hidden">
          <img src={`${base}images/features/decoturf-court.jpg`} alt="デコターフコート" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
        </div>
        <div class="text-white">
          <p class="text-accent font-bold tracking-[0.2em] text-sm mb-4">ABOUT US</p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-8 leading-tight">
            1人でも多くの方に<br />
            テニスの楽しさを。
          </h2>
          <div class="w-12 h-0.5 bg-accent mb-8"></div>
          <p class="text-white/70 leading-loose mb-8">
            御忍庭球塾は、PLACE OF SPORTS NEO のインドアデコターフコートを使用し、
            1レッスン最大6名の少人数制で一人ひとりに寄り添ったレッスンを提供しています。
            天候に左右されない快適な環境で、年間を通してテニスを楽しめます。
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6">
            <a href={`${base}courses`} class="border border-accent text-accent hover:bg-accent hover:text-primary-dark font-bold px-8 py-3 transition text-center tracking-wider text-sm">
              コース・料金
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== FEATURES ===== -->
  <section class="py-32 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center mb-20">
        <p class="text-[5rem] md:text-[7rem] font-black text-primary/5 leading-none -mb-6 md:-mb-8">FEATURES</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold relative">3つの特徴</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
        <div class="group">
          <div class="relative mb-8">
            <span class="text-[4rem] font-black text-accent/20 leading-none">01</span>
            <div class="w-12 h-0.5 bg-accent mt-2"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="aspect-[4/3] overflow-hidden mb-6">
            <img src={`${base}images/features/snapshot.jpg`} alt="少人数レッスン" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition duration-700" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">少人数制（最大6名）</h3>
          <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed text-sm">
            1レッスン最大6名まで。コーチの目が一人ひとりに行き届く環境で、確実に上達できます。
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="group">
          <div class="relative mb-8">
            <span class="text-[4rem] font-black text-accent/20 leading-none">02</span>
            <div class="w-12 h-0.5 bg-accent mt-2"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="aspect-[4/3] overflow-hidden mb-6">
            <img src={`${base}images/hero/court.jpg`} alt="デコターフコート" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition duration-700" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">デコターフコート</h3>
          <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed text-sm">
            PLACE OF SPORTS NEO のインドアデコターフコートを使用。天候に左右されない快適な環境です。
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="group">
          <div class="relative mb-8">
            <span class="text-[4rem] font-black text-accent/20 leading-none">03</span>
            <div class="w-12 h-0.5 bg-accent mt-2"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="aspect-[4/3] overflow-hidden mb-6">
            <img src={`${base}images/features/lesson-snapshot.png`} alt="動画で振り返り" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition duration-700" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">動画で振り返り</h3>
          <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed text-sm">
            レッスンを動画で撮影。自分のプレーを客観的に確認し、効率的にスキルアップできます。
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== GUT24 BANNER ===== -->
  <section class="relative py-32 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[#0a0a1a]"></div>
    <p class="absolute top-8 right-4 md:right-12 text-[5rem] md:text-[10rem] font-black text-white/[0.03] leading-none tracking-tight">GUT 24</p>
    <div class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="text-white order-2 md:order-1">
          <p class="text-accent font-bold tracking-[0.2em] text-sm mb-4">STRINGING SERVICE</p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-4">OSHINOBI GUT 24</h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-white/80 mb-2">24時間受付のガット張替サービス</p>
          <div class="w-12 h-0.5 bg-accent my-8"></div>
          <p class="text-white/50 mb-8 text-lg">JR白石駅北口 徒歩2分 ・ 全品工賃込み ・ 2,800円〜</p>
          <a href={`${base}gut24`} class="border border-accent text-accent hover:bg-accent hover:text-primary-dark font-bold px-10 py-4 transition inline-block tracking-wider">
            詳しく見る
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="flex justify-center order-1 md:order-2">
          <img src={`${base}images/logo/gut24-logo.png`} alt="OSHINOBI GUT 24" class="w-56 h-56 md:w-72 md:h-72 rounded-full shadow-2xl" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== YOUTUBE ===== -->
  <section class="py-32 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <p class="text-[5rem] md:text-[7rem] font-black text-primary/5 leading-none -mb-6 md:-mb-8">MOVIE</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold relative mb-4">ダブルスの技術を毎週配信中</h2>
        <p class="text-text-light">YouTubeチャンネルでレッスン技術動画を投稿しています</p>
      </div>
      <div class="aspect-video overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
        <iframe
          class="w-full h-full"
          src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/bXEScAkbFYI"
          title="テニス解説動画"
          frameborder="0"
          allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
          allowfullscreen
        ></iframe>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center mt-10">
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCKtgQuL9B0c8y42hHnx8JQQ" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-primary font-bold border-b border-primary pb-1 hover:opacity-70 transition inline-flex items-center gap-2">
          YouTubeチャンネルを見る <span class="text-lg">→</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== CTA ===== -->
  <section class="relative py-32 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <img src={`${base}images/hero/court.jpg`} alt="" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-primary-dark/90"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 text-center text-white">
      <p class="text-accent font-bold tracking-[0.2em] text-sm mb-6">TRIAL LESSON</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-6">体験レッスン受付中</h2>
      <div class="w-12 h-0.5 bg-accent mx-auto mb-8"></div>
      <p class="text-white/70 mb-12 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        一般月曜コース・一般木曜コースは体験受講が可能です。<br />
        初回 3,000円でお試しいただけます。
      </p>
      <a href="https://lin.ee/2CKErIS" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="border border-accent text-accent hover:bg-accent hover:text-primary-dark font-bold px-12 py-5 transition inline-block text-lg tracking-wider">
        LINE で体験を申し込む
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
